<FlowDocument xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
              ColumnWidth="400" FontSize="30" FontFamily="宋体"
              Foreground="Black">
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="36">定义：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="30">凑整调零法(一)，是指乘数接近整十、整百......时，可先将被乘数扩大整十、整百.....倍再减去（或加上）其零数（或差数）倍数乘数的一种求积方法。可运用乘法对减法的分配率进行速算。</Run>
        <LineBreak />
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="32">举例：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28">19×98=</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="28" Foreground="Black">解答：</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">19×98</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×(100-2)</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=19×100-19×2</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1900-38</Run>
    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph>
        <Run FontSize="24" Foreground="Black">=1862</Run>
    </Paragraph>
</FlowDocument>